    "Both the online and offline questionnaire surveys offered participants the opportunity to enter a prize-based lottery after completing the questions.",
    "This approach was implemented to incentivize active participation and enhance the quality of responses.",
    "The goal was to gain a more precise understanding of how environmental accidents influence Generation Z's purchasing behavior towards green apparel.",
    "10.3389/fpsyg.2024.1338702 Frontiers in Psychology 09 frontiersin.org",
    "These methods and strategies ensured sample diversity and representativeness to understand Gen Z consumers' purchase intentions and behaviors comprehensively."
